ArcFileSystemWatcherService maintains a list of file extension supported by MediaProvider, and it skips sending media scan request to ARC when a newly created or modified file's extension is not in the list. The current list of supported extension is outdated as it was taken from aosp-nougat codebase. This CL updates it with the supported extensions in P, R and T.
BUG=b:261826183 TEST=unit_tests --gtest_filter="ArcFileSystemWatcherUtilTest.*" TEST=Manually check that when a file with an extension in this list is TEST=added in MyFiles/Downloads, it soon appears in the "Recent" tab of TEST=Android Files app.
